name: Normie
description: Join the 7 billion normies of the world in total memecoin domination. Normie represents the regular person and the little experiences we’ve all shared. It’s all about the small things. There are 7 billion normies in the world and only 1 billion $NORM tokens. Norm is highly meme-able, can fit into every situation, and represent a day in the normal life of anyone. Join the normies, have fun, and get cozy.
